{"tid":417603,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一個只係想要真愛ge女仔","createTime":"2017-09-28T22:52:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-29T13:44:28.000Z","uid":97887,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1d8912f9b2e764aebe92d97884f57cc311e91cc1","tid":417603,"uid":97887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T22:52:46.000Z","msg":"又係我<br />\n好想呻<br />\n話說同bf想結婚<br />\n所以開始儲錢啦<br />\n咁bf又話壓力大<br />\n<br />\n但我明明計劃第時我份糧比完一半自己父母，<br />\n剩番比佢<br />\n<br />\n佢咁都話大壓力，之後因為咁話要博命搵錢<br />\n<br />\n但係方法就係賭，愈賭愈大，愈博愈大<br />\n<br />\n話佢又話唔溫柔<br />\n<br />\n我真係唔明，如果我咩都肯同佢分享，又大咩壓力<br />\n<br />\n我唔想佢一個揹哂壓力又唔聽我講<br />\n<br />\n...."},{"pid":"a5ca8fe612cb8a340e0e6628f47d51ef9718a113","tid":417603,"uid":2638,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T22:53:46.000Z","msg":"賭錢既男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6faae4981375e98328795a564bdd85f7bacd0878","tid":417603,"uid":101508,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T22:54:15.000Z","msg":"收隻賭仔收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 絲打及早抽身啦"},{"pid":"fd06efa5ace4cbd290d4694c037c94e3c142f97a","tid":417603,"uid":101508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T22:54:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫隻賭仔收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 絲打及早抽身啦</blockquote>"},{"pid":"5395fdfc38099c31ff7e22f4ae473d022239a0d0","tid":417603,"uid":97887,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T22:55:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>賭錢既男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢話有data分析，<br />\n但問心，我自己有讀stat<br />\n<br />\n我唔信賭有pattern<br />\n<br />\n真係咁d 數學prof 發左達啦"},{"pid":"52da84b8aa2e0c44cd74797f4214c5f084dc7f16","tid":417603,"uid":127272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T22:56:39.000Z","msg":"賭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />祝你好運"},{"pid":"48657df8c86e88b361ad004411fff924b0a0cd3a","tid":417603,"uid":117821,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T23:10:25.000Z","msg":"最撚憎賭錢既男人"},{"pid":"fd9ab1cd5f6cd37f8b5e045e6c52c913535d369a","tid":417603,"uid":112483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T23:14:57.000Z","msg":"全職賭仔? 賭開咩先"},{"pid":"a216d0d7692b62c451022ad704745f5ee39c9fac","tid":417603,"uid":143691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T03:01:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>賭錢既男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢話有data分析，<br />\n但問心，我自己有讀stat<br />\n<br />\n我唔信賭有pattern<br />\n<br />\n真係咁d 數學prof 發左達啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我有聽過(真係聽架炸) 有個Professor係教stat嘅，賭馬贏左一筆錢，但係之後俾人告。我聽完都唔明點解會咁。<br />\n不過呢就算真係有啲咩定律，我自己就信做莊一定贏～<br />\n講番男友，佢去賭錢其實我覺已經好差&hellip;<br />\n再講壓力，一係就你同佢嘅期望不平衡(你有90%想結，佢得50%想結/plan唔到幾時，呢種大差距會做成壓力)。第二就佢係啲小壓力都受唔住嘅人。第三就你真係俾好多好多壓力佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95580bf1abc1f674cafd5fd9eb1cc8548005939d","tid":417603,"uid":55519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T03:28:21.000Z","msg":"結婚呢啲野順其自然架 冇得plan冇得逼架"},{"pid":"e1ed3460ebc640c66377f1ae6d294aa70eefecdb","tid":417603,"uid":97887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T10:32:23.000Z","msg":"我無比壓力佢，我話遲少少結，佢嘈我話唔想太遲"},{"pid":"e40863374b231d4bc3877433eb9c846358ec37c8","tid":417603,"uid":25598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T10:42:47.000Z","msg":"佢一日唔戒賭 你哋一日都唔會有將來"},{"pid":"f561c23d558ba7e36fbcffbcb48d7ad5dae4f378","tid":417603,"uid":69016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T10:47:28.000Z","msg":"結婚大壓力咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  佢係因為要同你結所以大壓力咋"},{"pid":"0e2a9d3741c3a6c1b135178aee0c488a86585f97","tid":417603,"uid":75768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T11:12:58.000Z","msg":"賭仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算依家比你贏到，你估真係贏足一世呀。<br />\n遲早出事，請及早抽身。"},{"pid":"0bbc0a3ef4bbeeec915eb9bc1cca4028f95dc6d3","tid":417603,"uid":118642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T12:27:06.000Z","msg":"賭錢既男人都敢要<br />\n咁你快啲同佢結婚<br />\n造福世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8c2fbfcc43bb13f20485a2597e2bd07ff9d1119","tid":417603,"uid":53868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T13:44:28.000Z","msg":"遲早輸到貼地，你自己諗下仲跟唔跟佢"}]}